title: Everything You Need to Know About Skull and Bones
description:
Avast ye mateys! Ubisoft’s epic pirate adventure Skull and Bones is right around the corner. So strap on your eye patch and find your favourite parrot, because we're going to tell you everything you need to know before setting sail.

Presented by Ubisoft.

description:
Discover a place where magic is EPIC!!!

Disney and Epic Games are creating a new expansive and open games and entertainment universe connected to Fortnite.

#IGN #Gaming #Disney

title: Ex Astris - Official Gameplay Trailer
description: Take a look at gameplay, various locations, combat, and more from Ex Astris in this trailer for the upcoming real-time, turn-based hybrid 3D RPG. Assuming the role of an Investigator, you will set out on an extraterrestrial quest in the world of Allindo in Ex Astris. Ex Astris will be available on iOS and Android on February 27, 2024.

title: Moana 2 - Official First Look Announcement Trailer (2024)
description:
Walt Disney Animation Studios’ epic animated musical “Moana 2” takes audiences on an expansive new voyage with Moana, Maui and a brand-new crew of unlikely seafarers. After receiving an unexpected call from her wayfinding ancestors, Moana must journey to the far seas of Oceania and into dangerous, long-lost waters for an adventure unlike anything she’s ever faced. Directed by Dave Derrick Jr. with music by Grammy® winners Abigail Barlow and Emily Bear, Grammy nominee Opetaia Foa’i, and three-time Grammy winner Mark Mancina, “Moana 2” opens in theaters on Nov. 27, 2024.

#IGN #Disney #Moana2

title: Parish - Official Trailer (2024) Giancarlo Esposito
description:
Parish is a highly-anticipated six-episode crime thriller distributed by AMC Networks. 

In Parish, Esposito stars as Gracian “Gray” Parish, a family man and proud owner of a luxury car service in New Orleans. After his son is violently murdered and his business collapses, an encounter with an old friend from his days as a wheelman resurfaces old habits, sending Gray on a high-stakes collision course with a violent criminal syndicate.

Parish stars Giancarlo Esposito, Zackary Momoh, Paula Malcomson, Skeet Ulrich, Bonnie Mbuli, Ivan Mbakop, Arica Himmel, Bradley Whitford, Amanda Brugel, and more. The series is created by Danny Brocklehurst and Jim Poyser. Brocklehurst serves as co-creator and executive producer. Eduardo Javier Canto and Ryan Maldonado serve as showrunners and executive producers; Giancarlo Esposito also executive produces alongside Brocklehurst, Poyser, Theo Travers, Jolyon Symonds and David Morrissey for Scribbler Films, Josh Kesselman, Danny Sherman, Barry J

title: Rocket League x Star Wars - Official Mandalorian Mayhem Trailer
description: Rocket League is ushering in our favorite bounty hunters into the game. Players can access Star Wars Mandalorian-themed cars including Din Djarin, Bo Katan, The Armorer, Paz Vizsla, and Boba Fett. An all-new Low-Gravity limited-time mode is also available coming with the Mandalorian Mayhem event running from February 7 through February 21.

title: Dragon's Dogma 2 - Official Fighter Vocation Trailer
description:
Check out the latest trailer for Dragon's Dogma 2 for another look at the Fighter vocation in action from the upcoming action RPG. The Fighter vocation excels in melee combat, deftly wielding a sword and shield. Fighters can slice through enemy ranks and deliver powerful blows, while also using their shields to protect themselves and their allies.

Dragon's Dogma 2 will be available on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, and Steam on March 22, 2024.

#IGN #Gaming #DragonsDogma2

title: Overwatch 2: Champions  - Official Season 9 Trailer
description:
Overwatch 2 is ushering in Season 9 titled 'Champions' with plenty of new content to enjoy. Players can enjoy Ranked Play more transparently alongside new Jade Weapon rewards, and a rank of Champion. A new co-op event with Cosmic Crisis, a new Mythic Skin, and more are coming to Season 9 including a Cowboy Bebop collaboration tease. Overwatch 2 Season 9: Champions is launching on February 13.

#IGN #Gaming #Overwatch2

title: God of War Ragnarök: Valhalla: Tips for Surviving the Afterlife - IGN Game Prep
description:
The Norse Realms of God of War: Ragnarok are back thanks to the Valhalla DLC. This new rogue-lite mode provides new story content and combat challenges that encourage players to apply the skills they’ve learned to a randomized set of abilities and perks. 
So whether you’ve finished the game on Give Me God of War difficulty, or you're a first-time spartan looking to rage, here’s a list of tips to help you navigate the Afterlife in no time. Chase labor objectives, grab the healing stones, explore thoroughly for chests, opt for the resurrection stone upgrade, and prioritize yellow and red tears first!
Presented by: The United States Air Force

title: SPY x FAMILY CODE: White - Official Trailer (English Dub)
description:
INCOMING MISSION: Watch SPY x FAMILY CODE: White, only in theaters this April. Watch the new English trailer now!

He's a spy. She's an assassin. Together, Loid and Yor keep their double lives to themselves while pretending to be the perfect family. However, their adopted daughter Anya, a telepath, knows both of their exciting secrets unbeknownst to them. While under the guise of taking his family on a weekend winter getaway, Loid's attempt to make progress on his current mission Operation Strix proves difficult when Anya mistakenly gets involved and triggers events that threaten world peace!

title: Skull and Bones - Official PS5 Immersion Trailer
description:
Skull and Bones is a third-person open-world pirate game developed by Ubisoft Singapore. Players on PlayStation 5 can enjoy Ubisoft's latest release to go from pirate outcast to kingpin with 3D Audio, Adaptive Triggers, Haptic Feedback, and more. Skull and Bones is launching on February 16 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X/S, Amazon Luna, and PC.

description:
Lost Hellden is a new JRPG from a team of veteran genre developers that features a unique painted art style described as "Deep 2D" and promises a "strategic action battle system" along with a rich story, deep characters, and plenty of character customization. description:
C-Smash VRS, the VR love letter to the beloved Sega Dreamcast and arcade game, is coming to Meta Quest 2 and Quest 3 on April 4. 

Check out the new trailer.

title: A Quiet Place: Day One - Official Trailer (2024) Lupita Nyong’o, Joseph Quinn
description:
Discover why our world went quiet. Check out the tense trailer for A Quiet Place: Day One, an upcoming movie starring Lupita Nyong’o, Joseph Quinn, Alex Wolff and Djimon Hounsou. 

Allyson Seeger and Vicki Dee Rock serve as executive producers on A Quiet Place: Day One. It is produced by Michael Bay, Andrew Form, p.g.a., Brad Fuller, and John Krasinski. Based on characters created by Bryan Woods & Scott Beck. The story is by John Krasinski and Michael Sarnoski. The screenplay is by Michael Sarnoski.

A Quiet Place: Day One, directed by Michael Sarnoski, opens in US theaters on June 28, 2024, and is coming soon in UK cinemas.

#Movies #MovieTrailers #IGN

title: Lies of P x Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty - Official Collaboration Trailer
description:
Check out the Lies of P x Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty collaboration trailer for a look at the exclusive Azure Dragon Crescent Glaive weapon and Armor of the Honorable and Bandana of the Honorable costume. 

The collaboration between Neowiz's souls-like action RPG, Lies of P, and Koei Tecmo’s dark fantasy action RPG, Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty, will arrive as a free update for players starting February 14, 2024 on PlayStation 5 (PS5), PlayStation 4 (PS4), Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, Game Pass, and Steam.

#LiesOfP #WoLongFallenDynasty #Gaming

title: Final Fantasy 7 Rebirth Demo Gameplay Walkthrough - Nibelheim
description:
Check out this Final Fantasy 7 Rebirth Nibelheim gameplay walkthrough from the FF7 Rebirth demo. Cloud reminisces about a mission he undertook with the legendary SOLDIER Sephiroth in Cloud’s very own home town, Nibelheim. Featuring familiar iconic moments and brand new sections, this free demo (revealed during the State of Play showcase on February 6th) shows the start of Final Fantasy 7 Rebirth where Sephiroth is even a playable character, and progress will carry over to the main game if you complete the full “Fall of a Hero in Nibelheim” chapter.

The free demo will be updated with another gameplay segment set in Junon at a later date. Final Fantasy VII Rebirth releases on PS5 on February 29, 2024.

Imaginary - Official Trailer #2 (2024) DeWanda Wise, Tom Payne
description:
From Blumhouse, the genre-defining masterminds behind FIVE NIGHTS AT FREDDY’S and M3GAN, comes an original horror that taps into the innocence of imaginary friends – and begs the question: Are they really figments of childhood imagination or is something more terrifying lying just beneath?
 
When Jessica (DeWanda Wise) moves back into her childhood home with her family, her youngest
stepdaughter Alice (Pyper Braun) develops an eerie attachment to a stuffed bear named Chauncey
she finds in the basement. Alice starts playing games with Chauncey that begin playful and become
increasingly sinister.
 
As Alice’s behavior becomes more and more concerning, Jessica intervenes only to realize Chauncey is much more than the stuffed toy bear she believed him to be.

#IGN #Movies

description:
Watch our IGN Final Fantasy 7 Rebirth preview. FF7 Rebirth is layered with several new ideas that, at least across the duration of a recent three-hour playable demonstration, suggest Cloud and co’s upcoming journey will feel like a genuine sequel rather than a full-priced expansion.

Don't miss our FF7 Rebirth impressions, ahead of the PS5 game's release on February 29, 2024.

title: Final Fantasy 7 Rebirth: Migardsormr Gameplay and Comparison
description:
Check out this Final Fantasy 7 Rebirth gameplay and FF7 gameplay comparison! In FF7 Rebirth, the Migard Zolom, the giant snake now called Migardsormr makes his return. Unlike the original FF7, this fight is no longer skippable if you’re riding a Chocobo. What is the same though is the beast’s conclusion, with Rebirth telling the story of how Sephiroth managed to impale a 30-foot serpent on an even larger tree just like in the original. Let's check it out!

#FinalFantasy #Gaming #IGN
